# Override the SlimSAM-77 ONNX URLs if you want to self-host the models or
# point to a different quantized export. Defaults (used when unset) pull from
# the Xenova HuggingFace repo — a well-maintained public export.
#
# VITE_SAM_ENCODER_URL=https://huggingface.co/Xenova/slimsam-77-uniform/resolve/main/onnx/vision_encoder_quantized.onnx
# VITE_SAM_DECODER_URL=https://huggingface.co/Xenova/slimsam-77-uniform/resolve/main/onnx/prompt_encoder_mask_decoder_quantized.onnx
